            <title>[CSV-217] Add autoFlush option for CSVPrinter</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CSV-217</link>
                <project id="12313222" key="CSV">Commons CSV</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;CsvPrinter doesn&apos;t flush data on close. Looks like a bug, for me.&lt;/p&gt;

